leads.lead_text: Leaves 8–17 mm wide; inflorescence 4–6-branched; female heads mostly not subtended by leaf-like bract; fruits broadly obovoid, c. as wide as long
Leaves less than 5 (rarely to 9) mm wide; inflorescence unbranched or with 1–3 branches; female heads all subtended by a leaf-like bract; fruits narrowly obovoid, c. half as wide as long
